  <brief_title>Effect of CPAP Therapy on LPR Among Patients With OSAS</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of CPAP Therapy on Symptoms and Signs of Laryngopharyngeal Reflux Among Patients With Obstructive Sleep Apnea</official_title>
